s2_title:'Quick Start Guide',s2_install_title:'1. Install and Launch',s2_install_step1:'Download the installer for your platform from the download page.',s2_install_step2:'Run the installer (macOS: open the .dmg and drag to Applications; Windows: run the .exe installer).',s2_install_step3:'Launch ArtNet Manager from your applications.',s2_tip_guardian:'For production environments, enable Guardian Mode from the application menu to ensure automatic recovery from unexpected crashes.',
s2_receive_title:'2. Receive Signals',s2_receive_step1:'Signal reception starts automatically when the application launches.',s2_receive_step2:'Check the reception status on the Dashboard in the left sidebar.',s2_receive_step3:'When packets arrive from DMX sources on the network, active universes are displayed.',
s2_view_title:'3. View Channel Values',s2_view_step1:'Click Universes in the sidebar.',s2_view_step2:'Select a universe from the universe picker at the top.',s2_view_step3:'The 512-channel color grid updates in real time.',
s2_forward_title:'4. Set Up Forwarding',s2_forward_step1:'Click Forwarding in the sidebar.',s2_forward_step2:'Click Add Destination in the top right.',s2_forward_step3:'Configure the destination: Name, Target IP, Protocol (Art-Net or sACN), and Mode (All Universes or Selected Only).',s2_forward_step4:'Toggle the destination ON to start forwarding immediately.',
s2_export_title:'5. Export Settings',s2_export_step1:'Click the Export button on the Forwarding page.',s2_export_step2:'The configuration is saved as a JSON file.',s2_export_step3:'Use Import to migrate settings to another machine.',
